  "title": "Sales Support",
  "description": "<p><u>Sales Admin</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare quotations, stock status and follow ups</li>\n  <li>Assist in documentations and filing</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with Operations Division on order status</li>\n  <li>Update customers on order fulfilment and delivery</li>\n  <li>Verify customers’ billing names</li>\n  <li>Verify Payments Received</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Sales Support</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide customer service</li>\n  <li>Make arrangement for showroom visits and product training</li>\n  <li>Perform showroom duties and assist in slab markings</li>\n  <li>Prepare and replenish collateral like samples and catalogues</li>\n  <li>Handle ad hoc duties assigned</li>\n</ul>",
